OL,4,G0405FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe second visit is to The Flower
OL,6,     GPot in Sunbury-on-Thames, where
OL,7,     Gowner Simon and manager Pierre
OL,8,     Goffer their guests a stylish stay
OL,9,     Gand a game of real tennis at
OL,10,     GHampton Court Palace.
OL,11,G0435FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe third visit is to the Dolphin
OL,13,     GHotel in Exmouth, Devon, where
OL,14,     Gowner Jo takes her guests
OL,15,     Gpaintballing and to a floating
OL,16,     Grestaurant. But there are
OL,17,     Gsuspicions of game-playing.
