OL,4,G0500FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GPat and Nigel pride themselves on
OL,6,     Gtheir award-winning breakfast at
OL,7,     Gtheir B&B in Seaton, Devon. But
OL,8,     Gwill an afternoon spent town-
OL,9,     Gcrying entertain their guests?
OL,10,G0525FFour in a Bed
OL,11,     GWith all the visits over, the
OL,12,     GB&Bers come together to confront
OL,13,     Gtheir rivals and discover how
OL,14,     Gmuch they've been paid, before
OL,15,     Gthe winner is announced.
OL,16,G0555FKirstie's House of Craft
OL,17,     GKirstie Allsopp puts celebs to
OL,18,     Gthe test in crafting challenges.
OL,19,     GChris Hollins and Laura Hamilton
OL,20,     Gcraft colourful paper gift bags.
